 results so doing it well makes a difference greatest hr challengeobstacle ive found it really tough finding effective ways to dramatically change the culture of a company with a long history of success  and no immediate burning platform  to take advantage of the current and future marketplace challenges and opportunities changing deeprooted historical practices and a traditional mindset can be daunting and takes time newsletter signup benefits hr technology talent management hr leadership inside hr tech hrenow special offers email address privacy policy future goals i want to continue to ensure hr has top talent innovation marketbased practices and a global servicedelivery infrastructure to drive business results and help the company achieve its mission vision and longterm goals i also want to help children in underserved communities gain greater access to science technology engineering and math education   copyright  lrp publications most popular viewed shared biggest hcm deal for infor a notsoquiet problem noise looking ahead at the eeoc the lowperformer paradox a complete culture overhaul new evidence on minimum wages defiant and disrespectful pledging for diversity is the persuader rule in peril a wary welcome biggest hcm deal for infor looking ahead at the eeoc the lowperformer paradox pledging for diversity the adea at  a notsoquiet problem noise new evidence on minimum wages what good hr looks like a complete culture overhaul a wary welcome topics benefits news  opinion healthcare retirement disability employment law employment law stories legal clinic most powerful employment attorneys hr technology news  opinion hr technology conference top hr products hr leadership news  opinion people career center hr executive of the year hrs elite most admired for hr rising stars conferences talent management news  opinion performance management compensation talent acquisition relocation training and development conferences columns benefits column hr leadership column 